                <section>
                    <h>uses</h>
                    <section id="seoladh-obj">
                        <h>object</h>
                        <p><g>seòladh</g> can be used as the object of a verb – <ul>
                                <li><g><a href="?gd=cuir">cuir</a> seòladh air <a href="?gd=litir"
                                            >litir</a></g>
                                    <en>address a letter</en> –
                                <ul>
                                    <li>older pedagogical examples – <xl id="cuir-older-pedag">
                                        <li>
                                            <gd>Tha mo mhàthair a’ sgrìobhadh litreach gu m’athair a tha
                                                air falbh. Thubhairt mo mhàthair, “An téid thu do bhocsa
                                                nan litrichean leis an litir seo, Iain?” “Théid,” ars
                                                Iain, “falbhaidh mi an dràsda”. “Fuirich gus an dùin mi
                                                i is gus an <m>cuir mi seòladh oirre</m>. Ceannaich
                                                fhéin stamp agus cuir oirre i.” [...]</gd>
                                            <tr>My mother is writing a letter to my father who is away.
                                                My mother said, “Will you go to the postbox with this
                                                letter, John?” “Yes, I will,” said John, “I will leave
                                                now.” “Wait until I seal it and put an address on it.
                                                Buy a stamp and put it on it.”[...]</tr>
                                            <ref text="621">td. 5</ref>
                                        </li>
                                    </xl>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </p>
                    </section>
